DESCRIPTION
The ongoing rivalry between two sisters constantly fighting each other for the attentions of the boy next door. Starring Casey Calvert as the older more confident sister and Blair Williams as the younger sister with a chip on her shoulder who gets payback in the end. Ariella Ferrera and Marcus London are the loving parents of these dueling darlings, with Damon Dice as the initial heart throb and Tyler Nixon as the new boy who moves in next door
